# 🌟 Core Idea

VelocityVerse sirf racing game nahi hai.

Ye complete vehicle experience hai.

Player:

- 🚗 Drive kar sakta hai
- 🏎️ Race kar sakta hai
- 🏍️ Stunts kar sakta hai
- 🚤 Boat chala sakta hai
- 🚁 Helicopter uda sakta hai
- ✈️ Plane fly kar sakta hai

