# 🏆 Score System ⭐

Har activity score degi.

Examples:

Perfect Drift

+50

Perfect Jump

+75

Long Air Time

+100

Perfect Landing

+60

Clean Race

+150

Perfect Delivery

+80

No Crash Bonus

+120

---

# 🔥 Combo System

Ek ke baad ek stunt karoge to Combo banega.

Example

Drift

↓

Jump

↓

Flip

↓

Perfect Landing

Combo Bonus milta jayega.

---

# ⚡ Streak System ⭐

Agar player continuously achha perform kare bina crash kiye to Streak badhegi.

Example

🔥 5 Streak

Small Bonus

🔥 10 Streak

XP Bonus

🔥 20 Streak

Coin Bonus

🔥 30 Streak

Rare Reward Chance

🔥 50 Streak

Legend Driver Achievement

Crash hote hi Streak reset.

